{"tid":2352220,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[媽媽] 佩洛西連任美國眾議院議長","createTime":"2021-01-04T01:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T14:21:38.000Z","uid":57677,"like":22,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"19b35f6db0aba5a3decd73ae083886b2d95709ee","tid":2352220,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:05:33.000Z","msg":"美國國會展開新會期，眾議院繼續由民主黨控制，佩洛西一如所料，連任眾議院議長，但由於民主黨流失11席，加上有5名民主黨人未有支持佩洛西，令她的得票較上屆少。 佩洛西感謝民主黨人再次選擇她出任議長，她指國會在特別艱難的時刻展開新會期，當務之急是應對疫情，相信一定可以擊敗新型冠狀病毒。佩洛西又說，是時候讓國家康復，眾議員會與候任總統拜登和候任副總統賀錦麗合作，挽救更多生命和建立更公義的美國。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2373271\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2373271&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=c6791f27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2373271</a>"},{"pid":"1b2a7f95b9f2c8700526b2b679cbd93cd7125592","tid":2352220,"uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:16:13.000Z","msg":"廢登力邏輯<br />\n<br />\n民主黨內訌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967b032eea6b95adfe7ab9b628c08550ce152501","tid":2352220,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:17:32.000Z","msg":"佩洛閪"},{"pid":"78f570a7baffa5d7c3c3a1a44efcbaaf3c74bda8","tid":2352220,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:24:36.000Z","msg":"左膠好傷心"},{"pid":"3c579a829aaa87cf217c949e78dad44dcd61b9bd","tid":2352220,"uid":173207,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"78f570a7baffa5d7c3c3a1a44efcbaaf3c74bda8","tid":2352220,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:24:36.000Z","msg":"左膠好傷心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:28:43.000Z","msg":"佢哋愈傷心 